ygData.subject: Re: Druid in the Quellious Server
ygData.msgSnippet: Kyrianie! So nice to see you posting. Congratulations again on level. I hope you got it back. ;) Lake Rathe is an oustanding place to hunt...I
ygData.messageBody:
Kyrianie! So nice to see you posting.
<br><br>Congratulations again on level. I hope you got it back.
;)<br><br>Lake Rathe is an oustanding place to hunt...I stayed
there from 20-25, in group and solo. From there,
consider the Keep in HighPass Hold before moving on to
Cazic. You can fight in the Keep from 23-35, and then
start checking Cazic at about 25+. Cazic is good
hunting, but you can't beat the Keep for experience. Of
course, having food, merchants, and a bank right upstairs
makes it all the more appealing.<br><br>Send me a tell
in game if you're inclined. I'd like to hear from
you again. :)<br><br>May Tunare guide your way and
bless you always.<br><br><br>Murial Mayere<br>Druid of
Kelethin
